                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                langAttribute="none"
                                text="&lt;p>As a leader in the field of immunology, AbbVie is committed to supporting innovation that will continue to advance education and patient care for complex immunologic conditions.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>We provide educational support in the following areas:&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Addressing the burden of disease;Understanding new discoveries and new therapies in development; and&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Supporting capacity-building initiatives aimed at increasing the number of healthcare providers across immunology specialties.&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>We will consider requests in the following areas:&amp;nbsp;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>Rheumatology&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Ankylosing Spondylitis&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Psoriatic Arthritis&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Rheumatoid Arthritis&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Spondyloarthritis&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Systemic Lupus Erythematosus&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>Dermatology&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Atopic Dermatitis&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Psoriasis&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Psoriatic Arthritis&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Alopecia Areata&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Vitiligo&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>Gastroenterology&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Inflammatory Bowel Disease&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                            <item_1670862290361
                                cq:panelTitle="Oncology"
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2026-02-13T11:36:25.378-05:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>Combining our deep knowledge of biology with innovative technologies, AbbVie is committed to supporting education of scientific advances for those living with and treating widespread and debilitating cancers.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Oncology is a rapidly changing area. It is important to provide resources to help patients and healthcare providers navigate the evolving landscape of blood cancers and solid tumors.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>We provide educational support in the following areas:&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Staying abreast of the rapidly evolving cancer landscape and science;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Understanding the importance and relevance of biomarkers and cytogenetic testing;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Developing and enhancing skills aimed at a meaningful co-management of disease; and&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Improving communication between patients and care team members&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>We will consider requests in the following areas:&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>Hematologic Malignancies&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Acute Myeloid Leukemia&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Chronic Lymphocytic Leukemia&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Multiple Myeloma&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Blastic Plasmacytoid Dendritic Cell Neoplasm&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>Solid Tumors&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Ovarian Cancer&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                            <item_1670862294597
                                cq:panelTitle="Neuroscience"
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2024-08-26T14:23:05.698-04:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>Our goal is to provide education and support aimed at patients and &amp;nbsp;healthcare providers managing difficult-to-treat neurological diseases as well as urologic syndromes and dysfunction associated with these conditions.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>We&amp;nbsp;provide educational support in the following areas:&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Addressing the shortage of healthcare providers dedicated to the field of movement disorders; Understanding the staging of Parkinson’s Disease and corresponding appropriate therapies;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Educating patients and their care partners to be active and engaged participants in their care;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>New discoveries of neuroscience and new therapies in development.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>We will consider requests in the following areas:&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Migraine&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Chronic&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Episodic&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Preventative&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Psychiatry&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Bipolar Depression&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Major Depressive Disorder&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Parkinson’s Disease&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Spasticity/Movement Disorders&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                            <item_1672521782333
                                cq:panelTitle="Aesthetics"
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2022-12-31T16:42:24.863-05:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>With the increase in technological advances and the growing field of aesthetic medicine, we are committed to educating the healthcare community and their patients by supporting scientific, evidence-based initiatives.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>We provide educational support in the following areas:&lt;/b>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Supporting education on non-surgical and non-invasive techniques to achieve the best patient outcomes;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Enhancing clinician understanding of how to communicate, treat and manage patients; and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Supporting educational initiatives with the goal of achieving optimal outcomes for patients in breast implant-based surgery and acellular dermal matrix-based surgery.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>We will consider requests in the following areas:&lt;/b>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Non-Invasive Body Contouring&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Non-Surgical Facial Aesthetics&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Plastics and Regenerative Medicine&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                            <item_1672521785501
                                cq:panelTitle="Eye Care"
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2026-03-06T11:54:51.519-05:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="stromkx1"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                langAttribute="none"
                                text="&lt;p>New treatment modalities are a continuing process in improving vision care. We will support educational initiatives on the latest evidence and evolving landscape for eye care treatments.&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>We provide educational support in the following areas:&lt;/b>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Increasing understanding of the importance of early treatment and continuum of care with interventional Glaucoma (IG) mindset along the patient treatment journey.&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Educating healthcare providers on the current unmet needs and the burden of retinal diseases.&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Increase understanding of dry eye disease as a chronic multifactorial condition of the ocular surface.&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>We will consider requests in the following areas:&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/b>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Corneal Health (dry eye disease)&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Glaucoma (angle closure glaucoma, open angle glaucoma)&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Retina (wet age-related macular degeneration(wet AMD), diabetic macular edema, diabetic retinopathy, including gene therapy)&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                            <item_1672521788508
                                cq:panelTitle="Other Specialty Areas"
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2026-02-13T11:27:28.278-05:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>We are committed to improving the quality of life for patients with a focus on disease areas where significant unmet need still exists. For example, Exocrine Pancreatic Insufficiency/Pancreatitis.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                        </accordion>
